---
title: Zesty Romesco Striploin Steak with Smoky Potatoes and Garlicky Crouton Salad
description: Don't let the impressive name of this recipe fool you: this restaurant-quality meal with international flare comes together in just six steps! Spanish romesco sauce is traditionally made with bread and almonds, but we've moved those ingredients to the salad as crunchy toppers, while keeping the same zingy garlicky flavours!

Ingredients: Yellow potato • Striploin steak • Baby tomatoes • Ciabatta roll (unbleached untreated enriched wheat flour flour (wheat flour, niacin, reduced iron, thiamine mononitrate, riboflavin, folic acid), water, sea salt, yeast, malted barley flour) (barley, wheat) • Roasted red pepper pesto (roasted red pepper, soybean oil, water, sunflower seeds, garlic, parmesan cheese (milk, bacterial culture, salt, lipase, calcium chloride, microbial enzyme, powdered cellulose), modified corn starch, salt, sugar, herbs, citric acid, spices, xanthan gum, potassium sorbate) (milk) • Spring mix (lolla rosa multi-leaf lettuce, red flash red oak lettuce, red leaf multi-leaf lettuce, green oak lettuce, bally hoo tango lettuce) • Garlic spread (margarine (soybean oil, water, modified palm and palm kernel oils, salt, vegetable monoglycerides, soy lecithin, potassium sorbate, natural flavour, citric acid, annatto and turmeric, vitamin A palmitate, vitamin D2), garlic, onion powder, water, salt, vegetable mono and diglycerides, maltodextrin, citric acid, parsley, natural flavour, xanthan gum, potassium sorbate, natural colour, vitamin E) (soy) • Feta cheese (pasteurized milk, partly skimmed milk, water, salt, lipase, bacterial culture, microbial enzyme, cellulose, natamycin, calcium chloride) (milk) • Almonds • Red wine vinegar (wine vinegar, potassium sorbate, sulphites) (sulphites) • Parsley • Smoked paprika-garlic blend (smoked paprika, garlic powder, silicon dioxide) (sulphites) • Garlic.
